abstract: The network is intended to showcase the potential new uses of ultra-high-speed broadband networks.
snippet: The network is intended to showcase the potential new uses of ultra-high-speed broadband networks.
lead_paragraph: SAN FRANCISCO  Google said Wednesday that it would offer ultrahigh-speed Internet access in some communities in a test that could showcase the kinds of things that would be possible if the United States had faster broadband networks.

headline.main: Google Set to Showcase Fast Internet
headline.print_headline: Google Set To Showcase Fast Internet
